7883int
7884mapi_dissect_struct_DATA_BLOB(tvbuff_t *tvb _U___attribute__((unused)), int offset _U___attribute__((unused)), packet_info *pinfo _U___attribute__((unused)), proto_tree *parent_tree _U___attribute__((unused)), dcerpc_info* di _U___attribute__((unused)), guint8 *drep _U___attribute__((unused)), int hf_index _U___attribute__((unused)), guint32 param _U___attribute__((unused)))

7890 ALIGN_TO_4_BYTES{ if(!di->conformant_run) { if(offset&0x03) { offset=(

7903
7904 proto_item_set_len(item, offset-old_offset);
7905
